    "faq": {
      "eyebrow": "FAQ",
      "title": "Frequently asked questions",
      "items": [
        [
          "How does the AI plan work?",
          "LiveOn uses profile data to suggest meals, workouts, water and daily actions. The plan can be refined as you progress."
        ],
        [
          "How long does plan creation take?",
          "The first profile is designed for a fast start: you can get a basic plan in about 60 seconds."
        ],
        [
          "Can I use LiveOn free?",
          "Yes. The Free plan helps you get the first plan and try basic tracking."
        ],
        [
          "Is LiveOn good for weight loss?",
          "Yes, when selected as a goal. LiveOn considers calories, activity, meals and progress."
        ],
        [
          "Can I gain muscle with LiveOn?",
          "Yes. The plan can consider calorie surplus, protein and workout progression."
        ],
        [
          "Can I use it without a gym?",
          "Yes. You can choose home workouts and available equipment."
        ],
        [
          "Does LiveOn consider my budget?",
          "Yes. Budget is used when building the menu and shopping list."
        ],
        [
          "Can I exclude food I do not eat?",
          "Yes. Add allergies, constraints and disliked products."
        ],
        [
          "How does food photo analysis work?",
          "Photo analysis helps estimate a meal faster and add it to tracking."
        ],
        [
          "Is my data safe?",
          "Profile data is used for personalization and managed inside the service."
        ]
      ]
